quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  19,26,"Ñaam yaraa ɓuɓɓinaa gite, si a yi'ii goɗɗo immorde e ɓanndiŋke wi'u: "Miin dey mi takkanii Hinnorante(jurmotooɗo korka mi wowlidata e neɗɗaŋke hannde"."
  19,27,"O radi e makko ka yimɓe makko, homo tammbii mo ɓe wi'i: "Ko an yo Mariyama gooŋɗii a addii hu'unde hawnii nde"."
  19,28,"Eyma banndiraawo Haaruuna baaba maa laatanooki neɗɗo bonɗo neene maaɗa kadi laataaki jinoowo."
  19,29,"[Mariyama] joopii e makko, ɓe mbi'i:"Ko hono min njewtirta e on sanfaajo gonɗo e woofordu(liir) gondo e tiiggu"."
  19,30,"[Iisaa] maaki: "Miin dey ko mi jiyaaɗo Alla o okkii kam deftere nden o waɗii kam annabaajo"."
  19,31,"O waɗi kam Barkinaaɗo nokku kala ka mi woni, o wasiyii kam Juulde nden e Jakka on fodde miɗo wuuri."
  19,32,"Ko mi ɗigganɗo yumma am, o waɗaani kam ndunndarankeejo malkisaaɗo."
  19,33,"Kisal on wonii e am ñande mi jibinaa e ñande mi maayata e ñande mi immintintee ko mi guuruɗo."
  19,34,"On ko Iisaa geɗal Mariyama Daalol Goongawol ngol heɓe cikkitoo fii mu'um."
  19,35,"Haananaa Alla nde o jogitotoo ɓiɗɗo senaare e wonanii mo, si O ñaawii fiyaake o daalanay mo tan: "Won" o wona."
  19,36,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, mdewee o. Ko ɗum woni Laawol poocciingol"."
  19,37,"Pelle ɗe luutondiri hakkunde majji, bone wonanii ɓen yedduɓe ceedagol ñalaande mawnde."
  19,38,"Kaawee ko nanirta yi'ira wa maɓɓe Ñande ɓe aroyta e amen, kono tooñooɓe ɓen hannde heɓe e ndeer majjere ɓanngunde."